Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition
     On August 4, 2005, Assurant, Inc. issued a press release reporting on its financial results for the three and six months ended June 30, 2005 and 2004. The text of the press release, which is attached at Exhibit 99.1, and the statistical supplement which accompanied the press release, which is attached at Exhibit 99.2, are each incorporated by reference into this Item.
Exhibits
