An act of terrorism shall include any act, or preparation in respect of action, or threat of action designed to influence the government or of any nation or any political division thereof, or in pursuit of political, religious, ideological or similar purposes to intimidate the public or a section of the public of any nation by any person or group(s) of persons whether acting alone or on behalf of or in connection with any organization(s) or government(s) or , and which:
de jure
